Sammi Music Discord Bot - Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 10/5/2023

This Privacy Policy (hereinafter referred to as "the Policy") outlines how "Sammi Music" Discord bot (hereinafter referred to as "the Bot") collects, uses, and protects user data. By using the Bot, you consent to the practices described in this Policy.

1. Information We Collect

1.1 User Data: The Bot may collect and store user data as necessary for its operation, including but not limited to Discord user IDs and server information.

1.2 Usage Data: We may collect data on how you interact with the Bot, such as commands used and timestamps.

2. How We Use Your Data

2.1 We use the collected data to provide and improve the Bot's services, including personalized music recommendations and user experience enhancements.

2.2 We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your data to third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.

3. Data Security

3.1 We take reasonable measures to protect the data we collect from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

4. Data Retention

4.1 We retain user data only for as long as it is necessary for the purposes outlined in this Policy or as required by applicable laws.

5. Changes to the Policy

5.1 We may update this Policy from time to time. You will be notified of any significant changes, and your continued use of the Bot after such changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Policy.

6. Contact Information

6.1 If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or the data collected by the Bot, please contact us @dymtim on Discord.

7. Governing Law

7.1 This Privacy Policy shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United States.
